> "He kind of puts his, greataxe down and says."
> "He's, you know, he goes, we friend…"

**David Mendenhall** — *responding in character as Vukradin*
> "Lathander blesses you today, my child."

**GM** — *the orc's reaction*
> "Oh, you just said that? Oh, there was no magical… there was no magical…"
> "He's cool. He thinks that's awesome, and he's, like, just kind of walking away."
> "Lots to think about."
> "You know, he says, Talos offer power. Offender, more power."
> "Well, I found you."
> "He goes, follower of drought, drow, follow Lathander!"
> "He goes… Lathander, power, beyond doubt. Lathander, all-powerful."
> "And then he rushes towards… he rushes towards Valphine and say, I follow Drow Cleric of Lathander!"

**David Mendenhall** — *reacting*
> "Wow. We've got a follower!"

